# xkcd-improve-the-news

A Safari extension to improve the news, based on [xkcd 1288](http://xkcd.com/1288/). Code entirely stolen from [Cloud to Butt for Safari](https://github.com/logancollins/cloud-to-butt-safari).

[Download](#).
